com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Interface DeployCoreRoot

public interface DeployCoreRoot

A representation of the model object 'Deploy Core Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Annotation
  • Artifact
  • Artifact File
  • Capability
  • Capability Bundle
  • Capability Communication
  • Component
  • Unit
  • Config Topology
  • Constraint
  • Contract Explicit
